<Attribute name="Excess coverage nominal amount" id="35D459E6-6153-2963-83EE-9472F14C0393">
<createdBy>bosarie</createdBy>
<createdTime>2024-10-09 12:38:49 UTC</createdTime>
<comment><![CDATA[Excess coverage nominal amount is the amount in excess of the minimum coverage required with regards to the nominal amount in via the methodology of the Rating agency for the Covered bond programme.

Nominal amount is the sum of claims to payment of principal, determined in accordance with the respective statutory covered bond regime's rules that apply for determining sufficient coverage. ]]></comment>
