<Attribute name="Excess coverage present value(swap) / market value" id="83FDFF71-9E77-F944-AF21-5788A856F878">
<createdBy>bosarie</createdBy>
<createdTime>2024-10-09 12:42:24 UTC</createdTime>
<comment><![CDATA[Excess coverage present value(swap) / market value is the aggregate of the present value (swap) of the cover pool and the market value of the derived assets in the cover pool according to the rating agency. 

The asset-specific value is the economic value of the cover pool assets, as may be described by a fair value according to IFRS 13, a market value observable from executed transactions in liquid markets, or a present value that would discount future cash flows of an asset by an assetspecific interest rate curve.]]></comment>
